transcript:

Customer: Bihar karte hain. Haryana?
Customer: Haryana karte hain. UP?
Customer: UP karte hain. Jharkhand?
Customer: Karte hain.

Customer: Rajasthan ke alava acha.

Customer: Theek hai Rajasthan chhod dete hain theek hai Rajasthan chhod dete hain abhi Lotus Green indoor water fountain ki requirement aayi hui thi Agra se.

Customer: Abhi aap ye khud dekh lo na fiber aa gaya fiber mein kahan pe marble aata hai.
Executive: Chalo theek hai marble mein karna hai na theek hai.
Customer: Marble ki aapne aapko pata hai aapko marble ki dali hui hai fir aise kya kar rahe hain aap?
Executive: Nahi theek hai ek aadhi wo uske andar se not relevant mark ho jayegi koi dikkat nahi hai uske andar.
Customer: Haan yahi to baat hai na aapko samjha nahi hai main.
Executive: Abhi white marble white marble temple ki requirement aayi thi 41 minute pehle Maharashtra Raigarh se.
Customer: Haan to wo fir aayi thi 5 feet marble water fountain ki aayi thi 46 minute pehle aayi thi ye.
Executive: Achchi kar rahe hain.
Customer: Fir white Ganesh statue ki aayi thi Solapur se requirement ek ghante pehle. Haan. To ye aati hai to kya hai ki desktop pe apne show nahi ho rahi hai iske aane se ya na aane se apan ko fark nahi padta hai.
Executive: Nahi aapke account bata raha hun to sold out ho gayi hai sold out dikha raha hai sari. Haan ye sold out ye aisa ye hai ki apne desktop pe show nahi ho rahi hai ab ye to sold out ho to kya matlab hai apne apne paas to hai nahi.
Executive: To usme kya hota hai ki sold out ka matlab ye nahi hai ki apne paas se wapas aayegi. Haan usme kya hota hai ki apne baat karke ispe to koi hai nahi ki apan sold out apni problem ho sakti hai ki apan sold out dekh ke liye. Sir wo sold out to sabhi ke liye hai na aisa nahi ki aapke liye special panel hai wo sold out ka agar ek buy lead panch logo ko consume kar liye to aap se jaldi fastest five logo ne consume kar liya to fir wo sold out wale bucket mein chale le jate hain ye aisa nahi hai ki aapke liye kar rahe hain hum log ye India Mart mein sabhi ke liye same option hai.
Customer: Haan ye main aapki baat barabar hai. But sari ki sari apne paas show nahi ho rahi hai. Ye kya karan hai?
Executive: Sir aati hai iski lead aati hai lekin supplier base bahut jyada hai aate hi wo kuch second ke andar consume ho jati hai.
Customer: Second mein consume ho jati hai sari ki sari.
Executive: Achcha achcha. To fir aap iska to usme usme aapko hyper active rehna padega bahut jyada active rehna padega aapko India Mart pe. Achcha achcha ki ki jaise hi aaye aap India Mart khol ke rakho kyuki lead aati rehti hai aisa nahi ki kya naam hai do ek din mein do aa rahi hai teen aa rahi hai aisa bhi nahi hai ghanto mein aa rahi hai lead sir. To aapko usme bahut jyada active rehna padega sir aapko highly active rehna padega. Bilkul bilkul kyuki ek to aap basic package ke andar ho sabse badi baat hai theek hai. To
Customer: Bhaiya aapne bhi dilaya to ye to hai nahi ki humne liye. Nahi nahi main sirf bata raha hun main aapko sahab to aapko jyada active jo hai buy lead pe rehna padega kyuki agar BCBT ke upar bani hogi to inquiry aa jayegi ya call aa jayegi to buy lead wala madhyam se pe aapko bahut jyada apne aap ko highly active rakhna padega iske andar sir. Ki mere paas turant lead aayi turant maine consume karke maine baat chit kar li uske upar. Bilkul kyuki aapka jo product hai sir sir do jagah banta hai aapka ye white marble jo temple hai Makrana mein aur ek aapka jo location hai Nagaur mein. Haan haan. To ye main do hi ghar hain sir apne paas yahan ke. Haan. To usme aapko hyper active rehna padega. Chalo. Sir ye wali baat hai aur koi jyada wo nahi hai matlab is cheez ke andar sir. To main aapke kal karta hun baat fir aapke topic mein dekhte hain. Haan ji? Kal karta hun main aapse baat fir dekhte hain ruko abhi. Baki koi issue?
